{"tid":1445870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武力唔升級，做咩都係輸","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:17.000Z","uid":73281,"like":96,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a731ae7f23a59ed4b858a3e15c2afdf751820a8f","tid":1445870,"uid":73281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"對家而家肆意使用武力，不斷升級毫無後果，而且清得愈黎愈快，愈黎愈強硬。義士不斷比人捉，我地只會愈黎愈少人，到時咩文宣，和理非，仲有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n2個月以黎我地文宣，證據，相同片，仲未夠多咩？但到而家有咩作用。我唔係話文宣冇用，但係革命底下文宣只係一個輔助，欠缺主導既武力制住對家，我地點都唔會贏。<br />\n<br />\n下個雞尾酒，唔好再掟入警署或者警車，直接掟向敵人好嗎？"},{"pid":"f9aafe2e5035215bad6baad084c67115d97a6e5b","tid":1445870,"uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔好覆呢個 post<br />\n<br />\n任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/QMniBV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/QMniBV</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不推文回覆"},{"pid":"513606256ac11fc5baef147d06219229bc969205","tid":1445870,"uid":73281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"自推！！"},{"pid":"e276602404fbc68185e9e31a573e01dc9877c1e7","tid":1445870,"uid":167878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n和理非要癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e0a899a6306359f54198baf22c3cdb9f89e4955","tid":1445870,"uid":73281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"自推！！！"},{"pid":"aeb6e5fb8b34b94d745cf5fa094e643ebbed2753","tid":1445870,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-